messages.messageBody:
Hi Sandra:

Thank you, thank you, so much for the information... I needed to hear what
you had to say to realize that it's gradual and in time I will be more
comfortable with what I'm doing.... On to read what others are saying.

Dawn
Unschooled kids are also making a model of the universe inside them, but

they're making it their own way, and they're not valuing the school-bits
over

the bits that their model has which are unique to them and their own
personal

interests and experiences - Sandra
